## Problem Statement

* Manual cluster-by-cluster capacity checks
* Time-consuming data collection and reporting
* Delayed visibility into capacity risks
* Garbage collection issues not centrally tracked
* Lack of consolidated cluster-wide reporting

## Solution Overview

* Automated capacity data collection via Dynatrace workflow
* Centralized visibility across all Cohesity clusters
* Threshold-based status classification (Healthy/Warning/Critical)
* Garbage collection metrics included in reporting
* Scheduled email reporting for operational visibility
